node.text: Happy Monday y’all!🤠🔥 Hope you have a great week!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katherine Salom in Ludington, Michigan with @officialmauijim, @captmwilliams, @xtratuf, @renegadeproductsusa, and @glakesgear. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Look at this 21 pound King Salmon I caught on Lake Michigan!🔥 This fish helped our team secure the win at the local Ludington boat club tournament! 🏆 Fishing on Lake Michigan with @renegadeproductsusa and @glakesgear aboard the Silver Addiction this week was an INCREDIBLE experience!🙌🏻 Have you ever caught a salmon?! 🎣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katherine Salom in Ludington, Michigan with @officialmauijim, @captmwilliams, @renegadeproductsusa, and @glakesgear. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text: Fished the Great Lakes for the first time today with @renegadeproductsusa and had an absolutely amazing time!🙌🏻 Got my first lake trout and had a blast reeling him in! Let me know if you have any tips on how to take fish home on a plane - I can’t wait to get this meat home and do some cooking!🎣
